-Seung…
-Seung-kyu.

45
00:02:53,006 --> 00:02:54,424
-Seung-kyu.
-Seung-kyu.

46
00:02:55,092 --> 00:02:56,676
Seung-kyu!

47
00:02:56,760 --> 00:02:58,428
-Seung-kyu!
-Seung-kyu.

