Sir.

84
00:05:09,434 --> 00:05:10,435
<i><font color="white">What is she doing?</font></i>

85
00:05:11,019 --> 00:05:13,563
I don't know. She's in her room.

86
00:05:13,647 --> 00:05:15,732
