88
00:05:17,359 --> 00:05:19,402
Just let her be. Yes.

89
00:05:19,486 --> 00:05:21,738
Call me if anything happens, okay?

90
00:05:21,822 --> 00:05:24,658
All right. See you tonight. Bye.

91
00:05:41,716 --> 00:05:44,553
