with the general election coming up.

94
00:05:55,272 --> 00:05:56,314
Let her stay here.

95
00:05:57,274 --> 00:05:58,692
That lowers the risk,

96
00:05:58,775 --> 00:06:01,194
and she may be helpful to us.

97
00:06:03,071 --> 00:06:04,531
